### (Admin) Login to create API client
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "replace_me"
}

### (Admin) Create API client (requires admin token)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/api-clients
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Integration",
  "clientId": "my-integration-app",
  "clientSecret": "REPLACE_WITH_STRONG_SECRET",
  "scopes": "cr:read cr:write",
  "active": true
}

### (Consumer) Get client token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/client-token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-Id: smoke-001

{
  "clientId": "my-integration-app",
  "clientSecret": "REPLACE_WITH_STRONG_SECRET"
}

### (Consumer) List CRs
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/crs/list
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-Id: smoke-002

{
  "filters": { "active": true },
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 20,
  "sort": { "field": "updatedAt", "direction": "desc" }
}

### (Consumer) List CRs in warranty period (milestone filter v1.1)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/crs/list
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-Id: smoke-002b

{
  "filters": {
    "milestone": ["Live (Warranty Period)"],
    "status": ["LIVE"]
  },
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 20
}

### (Consumer) Update CR to Fully Live (requires endDate)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/crs/{{cr_initiative_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-Id: smoke-003

{
  "status": "Live",
  "milestone": "Fully Live",
  "endDate": "2026-05-13"
}

### (Consumer) PATCH Fully Live without endDate — expect 400
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/crs/{{cr_initiative_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-Id: smoke-003b

{
  "status": "Live",
  "milestone": "Fully Live"
}

